name: Tribe Elders ~ Nana Imani
description:
As tragic as the passing of her mother's and grandmothers may have been, she knew she was born of an alternate kind. 
A ripple in the ocean moved a breath further at the time of her incarnation.
She was the seed of all mankind and the generations thereafter rolled into one.
Her face calm.
Her nerves settled.
As for Mother nature, this is her greatest example.
